description: Shrink Film
short_description: Crystal clear Durable Ideal for high speed application
summary: CWC shrink polyolefin film is a new polyolefin shrink film for a wide range of packaging applications. The innovative crosslink process provides strong, durable seals and excellent shrinkage. Optical properties are superior. This film exhibits outstanding abuse resistance and is easy to use. 701 is designed for use with L bar sealers along and high speed side seal machines.

description: Nylon Seine Twine Braided
short_description: Resists abrasion, mildew and most chemicals Construction twine Come in 4, 8 and 16 oz tubes
summary: Also known as mason twine, CWC seine twine has a smooth braided jacket that resists abrasion, holds chalk well and can be used for net repair and trotlines, making it popular in the construction and fishing industries. The synthetic fiber construction lasts longer than cotton and resists rot, mildew, petroleum products and most common chemicals.
